<h2 id="toc0"><span>Have comments on this year's JamCon? Submit your feedback <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-13206682/144-hour-jam-contest-two-feedback">here</a>!</span></h2>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>Come on and slam&#8230;</span></h1>
<p>And welcome to the second 144-Hour Jam Contest!</p>
<p>A jam contest, you say? What's that?</p>
<p>It's simple. From March 9th through March 15th, you will write three stories over a six-day period, competing for honor, glory, and meaningless prizes. This contest is designed to squeeze inspiration out of you and see what kind of works you can produce in an accelerated timeframe.</p>
<h1 id="toc2"><span>The Winners</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc3"><span>The 2020&#160;144-Hour Jam Contest Two <span style="color: gold"><strong>THEME GRAND PRIZE</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608432230" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;">Rounderhouse</a></span>, who submitted an entry for each theme and secured a total of 396 upvotes:</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-5983">SCP-5983</a> (&quot;Nuke York, Nuke York&quot;) (+140) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 1</span></li>
<li><a href="/adoption-poster-pearl">Adoption Poster: Pearl!</a> (+117) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5149">SCP-5149</a> (&quot;None of us are blind, Joe&quot;) (+139) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 3</span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="toc4"><span>The 2020&#160;144-Hour Jam Contest Two <span style="color: gold"><strong>FORMAT GRAND PRIZE</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608432230" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, who submitted an SCP, Tale, and GoI Format and secured a total of 175 upvotes:</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/cool-guys-dont-look-at-explosions">Cool Guys Don't Look At Explosions</a> (+82) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 1</span></li>
